snippet.title: Multicolored Zebra stripes - Twitch Plays Conway's Game of Life - Sir Robin Edition
snippet.description:
Play Conway's Game of Life by typing commands in the Twitch chat: https://www.twitch.tv/bzh314
@qwertyasdfuiopghjkl (https://www.twitch.tv/qwertyasdfuiopghjkl) disturbs the blue Zebra stripes (http://www.conwaylife.com/wiki/Zebra_stripes) set by @Glacier_nester (https://www.twitch.tv/glacier_nester) to add orange to the mix and take over.

More:
* VOD with chat commands: https://www.twitch.tv/videos/340747527
* Homepage of Twitch Plays Conway's Game of Life: https://bzh314.com/twitch_plays_conway_game_of_life/
* TPCGOL is built with the Unity3d Entity Component System (ECS)
* Play #TwitchPlaysGameOfLife Now on #Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/bzh314
